Reflex.SayString: I thank ye, Lord Mobiko, for saving this Kingdom. I daresay the forces of Chaos are gathering. I fear thine quest hath just begun! Seek out Master Koduwan in the Parallaxian Mountains, master his techniques, and rescue the World!!
Two red Coins be th'toll, yar

Lord Mobiko, you must hurry to the Castle!! Collect as many coins as possible and meet me at the Bay. Use the gamepad left stick and <a> button or [left] [right] and [space] on your <keyboard>keyboard to move and jump.
